node.text: I seriously feel tat how nice if i stay next to ur house

Few weeks back #neriya rules #poatta & today  as per our #data we are almost / for now done with the corona #gallata 😊. So Circuit breaker  #tata. Phase 1 begins...
.
But still - Ny's batch is still on HBL & #aathukaarar  #aapice key is #badhirama kept in bank locker .. So not much change...
.
On my plate,
💮Keerai masiyal
💮Ladies finger potato roast
💮Pepper rasam
💮Thai mango
💮Jackfruit payasam - combined shoot with Amma, coming soon
.
.
.
.
#circuitbreakersg #sgfood #friday #icookedthis #soulfood #homecooked #southindianfood #potatoroast #coronachronicles #sgfoodie #homefood #frommykitchen
👍 yummy plate... Every reason to have payasam and celebrate! U r exiting phase 1! We are entering phase one from tomorrow! Hope things work out for good🥺
My favorite jackfruit paayasam along with mango....such a yummm platter 😍😍
That’s a colorful delicious meal. So balcony pic 😉
Its raining jackfruit payasam in ig. Ellarum pottu thakarele @cookingfromheart idhu nyayama
@aashkamandal62 thank you so much.  Glad you watch my videos ❤️

I love your plating style so authentic. I visited south about 35 years ago and had diff south Indian food. You brought back those nostalgic memories. In this fast pace people have twisted plating so much that food looks good but loose authentic look. We eat by eyes and brain. So your plating style is so harmonized. ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️I do not know the language but I watch most of your video.🙏🙏
@shivarevathi nice to meet you here.. 😊 oh school opened there also .
@neeskitchen yes I'm here Sg north side😊

Hi Nees I'm your long time follower in youtube,but not met in insta,..I don know y I was not come in insta,..but I saw your posting sometimes or while I was here,nice posting daily updates interesting...👍🏻👌🏻 here I too jolly my elder girl went school, younger boy n aathukarar @home😅😅😊🌷💕
I seriously feel tat how nice if i stay next to ur house
